OL,6,FITV News Central correspondent Rajiv
OL,7,FPopat reports.
OL,9,FA 17-year-old who was refused a place
OL,10,Fin the army because two members of her
OL,11,Ffamily have had breast cancer has now
OL,12,Fbeen told she can join.
OL,14,FCarys Holmes performed well at the
OL,15,Ftough three-day selection camp at
OL,16,FWhittington Barracks in only to be
OL,17,Ftold she was being rejected because of
OL,18,Fa history of cancer in her family.
