OL,3,CTeen refused place in army because mum
OL,4,Cand aunt had breast cancer
OL,6,FHer family appealed and asked NHS
OL,7,Fgenetic experts to assess the chances
OL,8,Fof her developing breast cancer and
OL,9,Finheriting a gene called Brac1 .
OL,11,FThey said the risk of that before the
OL,12,Fage of 30 was extremely low.
OL,14,FThe Army has since done a U-turn and
OL,15,Fadmitted they made a mistake and have
OL,16,Fnow accepted her application.
OL,18,FThe Army told ITV News Central that
OL,19,Ffollowing a review of Carys' case, it
OL,20,Fconcluded that her rejection as
OL,21,Fmedically unfit was incorrect.
