OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We've reviewed the circumstances of
OL,8,Fthe case and are pleased to confirm
OL,9,Fthat Carys has been passed as
OL,10,Fmedically fit to join the Army.
OL,12,F"We apologise to Carys for the
OL,13,Fdifficulties she's experienced in her
OL,14,Fapplication so far."
OL,16,FHer new adventure and journey starts
OL,17,Fin October.
